			</distracter>
			<distracter oae-label="#4">
				<![CDATA[]]>
			</distracter>
			<distracter oae-label="#5">
				<![CDATA[]]>
			</distracter>
			<distracter oae-label="#6">
				<![CDATA[]]>
			</distracter>
		</distracters>
	</page>
	<page>
		<audio oae-label="audio file name (optional). Please include the file extension (.mp3)" oae-type="textarea" oae-rows="1">
			<![CDATA[]]>
		</audio>
		<text oae-label="Text" oae-type="textarea" oae-rows="25">
			<![CDATA[<b>A:</b>	Hi, Vera.  Did you do anything special last weekend? 
<b>B:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="Let me think.... Oh, yeah.  I went bike riding with my family." align="left"/>
<b>A:</b>	Sounds great. 
<b>B:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="What did you do?" align="left"/>
<b>A:</b>	I didn't do anything special.  On Sunday, I went for a walk.
<b>B:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="That sounds nice. The weather was beautiful." align="left"/>
<b>A:</b>	Yes, it was.]]>
		</text>

